<h3 class="text-2xl font-headline font-bold mb-4">What Does BMI Measure?</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-6">
                                Body Mass Index (BMI) is a person’s weight in kilograms divided by the square of height in meters. It is an inexpensive and easy screening method for weight category—underweight, healthy weight, overweight, and obesity.
                            </p>
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold hover:gap-3 transition-all cursor-pointer">
<span>Learn about screening vs diagnostic</span>
