<h2 class="text-3xl font-headline font-bold mb-6">Bias &amp; Limitations</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    While BMI is a useful population-level screening tool, it has significant limitations for individual assessment. It does not distinguish between excess fat, muscle, or bone mass, nor does it provide any indication of the distribution of fat among individuals.
                </p>
